{"tid":1585933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要做既唔係指責私了 而係要幫手拆掂佢/解釋/做好形象","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:21:05.000Z","uid":69525,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8be159eb57c3ab6a9523f6a40bca6f097c5d3b00","tid":1585933,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"［有圖］荃灣手足比人斬到開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471792</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌人私了之前唔該同我睇返呢個POST<br />\n又話要還眼 又話要黑警死全家<br />\n一隻眼都未還 一隻popo都未死<br />\n就想係到割<br />\n成日話唔割唔割 最撚快割就係班左膠大愛撚<br />\n政府都唔撚同班黑警割喇 你地點解要割? <br />\n<br />\n記住最重要既一點<br />\n手足永遠唔會主動郁手 永遠都係被動果一方<br />\n大家要做既野唔係指責 <br />\n而係要幫手拆掂佢同解釋 做返好做形象<br />\n咁勇武做野先叫做無後顧之憂 okay?<br />\n唔好再分化喇 推行動post喇<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議左膠撚 <br />\n印荃灣被斬手足果兩張圖警剔下自已 咁撚善忘<br />\n<br />\n辛苦所有遠征大西北既手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8109580424d60b0dbde972323cd1c7fc79cece26","tid":1585933,"uid":276839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"淨係識打啊伯，做閪咩。"},{"pid":"194a1e447ca744ed5638406bcf11f85b9fdeb846","tid":1585933,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8109580424d60b0dbde972323cd1c7fc79cece26","tid":1585933,"uid":276839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"淨係識打啊伯，做閪咩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野姐你"},{"pid":"48aa0fad9fbe60264e5002f1052a3919ef919967","tid":1585933,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">[文宣] 示威者９２２＂元朗＂自衛係因為知道警察將會同７２１一樣放任黑社會打市民！</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585810</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hk